{"tid":252114,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"皮革手縫銀包全攻略(2)-送手鐲篇","createTime":"2017-05-21T13:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T14:13:38.000Z","uid":61676,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"893e11b0ccc5699ade26f0290554e57e6b2aba70","tid":252114,"uid":61676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"事源我係上個po 教左大家做銀包<br />\n<br />\n皮革手縫銀包全攻略(新手篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/243927/page/9?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/243927/page/9?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n為左多啲人睇到同埋受惠 我決定開新po<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>[quote]多謝哂咁多位巴絲既支持 係小弟咁慢咁出都會幫我正評同推po 仲有啲巴絲會tg我叫我加油 實在係萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦都多謝搵我整野既巴絲啦 會盡快起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點</span></span>終於黎 為左多謝大家幫我推po 而我發現雖然個po係教銀包 但最多人問既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手鐲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/203311_d86c62c74b3731baa29402bcfa05a5ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F203311_d86c62c74b3731baa29402bcfa05a5ed.jpg&h=8e5043ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/203311_5b17c8f1cc0cbd38f86d1cba24b607cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F203311_5b17c8f1cc0cbd38f86d1cba24b607cb.jpg&h=dbdc78c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我決定<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">送(幾)隻出黎</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n你只要做既係 留你tg係到 <br />\n我會係一星期後 即係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">27號2359</span></span>截數 抽完就會聯絡你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">如果有30個人留低tg 我會送第2隻 即係30人留 抽2個 60人留 抽3個 上限係4個</span><br />\n<br />\n到時可以刻埋名 同你再講啦 中你先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後賣一賣廣告，唔鐘意就負評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以follow 我Ig impossible_leather <br />\n我會更新多啲作品出黎<br />\n<br />\n直接搵我就tg <a href=\"https://t.me/iameric123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiameric123&d=orEqo2PDfTnkAfc6t3i5rv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=25fb37d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iameric123</a><br />\n<br />\n一星期後見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>鐘意既就比多幾個正評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲有機會就再見<br />\n送手鐲都要時間做 每隻都要3小時咁上下<br />\n希望大家支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經盡量令大家feel comfortable 地賣廣告 <br />\n希望諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c494f0957224d0c3030a02a71df3eab725bf8d26","tid":252114,"uid":61676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"elvieeee_e<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hollypanghy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhollypanghy&d=orEqo2PDfTnkAfc6t3i5rv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f7e7de23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hollypanghy</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/chanki1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchanki1&d=orEqo2PDfTnkAfc6t3i5rv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fc29e30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/chanki1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kristylyt\" data-sr-url=